The paper presents a new PAC-Bayesian generalization bound that improves upon existing bounds and connects to excess risk bounds under Bernstein conditions. This suggests that the paper is likely to be related to machine learning (cs.LG), information theory (cs.IT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and statistics (cs.ST).
